Components.Label: Bill3
Components.Query:
WITH Sumcont AS (
    SELECT 
        SUM(ct1.PKG) AS PKG1,
		SUM(ct1.Weight) AS weight1,
		SUM(ct1.CBM) AS cbm1
		 
        
    FROM dbo.EntityContainer ct1
    LEFT JOIN dbo.Shipment sm1 ON ct1.EntityId = sm1.Id
    WHERE sm1.Id = '{Id}'
    GROUP BY sm1.Id
)
SELECT 
ISNULL(sm.HblNo,'') AS HBLNo,
ISNULL(sm.ShipperDes,'') AS shippertext, 
ISNULL(sm.ConsigneeDes,'') AS consigneetext, 
ISNULL(sm.NotifyPartyDes,'') AS NotyDes,
ISNULL(sm.Vessel,'') AS Feedervessel,
ISNULL(POl.Name,'') AS POLName,
ISNULL(POD.Name,'') AS PODName,
ISNULL(destination.Name,'') AS Destination,
isnull(payableat.Name,'') as Payable,
isnull(sm.NumberOriginalIdText,'') AS numberbill,
ISNULL(sm.ShippingMark,'') AS SPMK,
ISNULL(sm.DetailsGoods,'') AS DetailsGoodstext,
ISNULL( sm.ForDeliveryGoodsDes,'') AS Deliverygoods,
ISNULL(charge.Name,'') AS Chageterm,
ISNULL(place.Name,'') AS placeissue,

FORMAT(ISNULL(sm.IssueDate,''),'dd MMM, yy') AS dateissue,
ISNULL(receipt.Name,'') AS placereceipt,
ISNULL(deliveryplace.Name,'') AS deliveryplace ,
ISNULL(typemove.Name,'') AS Typeofmove,
ISNULL(caluse.Name,'') AS clause,
FORMAT(ISNULL(sm.SaillingDate,''),'dd MMM, yyyy') AS saillingdate,
ISNULL(sm.ContainerText,'') AS quantityofcontainer,
ISNULL(unit.Name,'') AS Unitpkg,

FORMAT((SELECT PKG1 FROM Sumcont WHERE Sumcont.PKG1 IS NOT NULL),'N{CTotalPrice}') AS sumpkg,
FORMAT((SELECT weight1 FROM Sumcont WHERE Sumcont.weight1 IS NOT NULL ),'N{CTotalPrice}') AS sumweight,
FORMAT((SELECT cbm1 FROM Sumcont WHERE Sumcont.cbm1 IS NOT NULL),'N{CTotalPrice}') AS sumcbm

FROM dbo.Shipment sm LEFT JOIN dbo.Terminal POL ON POL.Id = sm.PolId
LEFT JOIN dbo.Terminal POD ON POD.Id = sm.PodId
LEFT JOIN dbo.Terminal destination ON destination.Id = sm.FinalDestinationId
LEFT JOIN dbo.MasterData payableat ON payableat.Id = sm.FreightPayableId
LEFT JOIN dbo.MasterData charge ON charge.Id = sm.FreightChargeId
LEFT JOIN dbo.MasterData place ON place.Id = sm.PlaceIssueId 
LEFT JOIN dbo.Terminal receipt ON receipt.Id = sm.PlaceReceiptId
LEFT JOIN dbo.Terminal deliveryplace ON deliveryplace.Id = sm.PlaceDeliveryId
LEFT JOIN dbo.MasterData typemove ON typemove.Id = sm.TypeMoveId
LEFT JOIN dbo.MasterData caluse ON caluse.Id = sm.ClauseId
LEFT JOIN dbo.MasterData unit ON unit.Id=sm.UnitId
WHERE   sm.Id='{Id}' 

SELECT 
ISNULL(contype.Name,'') AS consize,
ISNULL(ct.ContainerNo,'') AS ContNo,
ISNULL(ct.SealNo,'') AS Seal,
format(ISNULL(ct.PKG,''),'N{CTotalPrice}') AS Qty,
ISNULL(unit.Name,'') AS Unit,
format(ISNULL(ct.Weight,''),'N{CTotalPrice}') AS GW,
format(ISNULL(ct.CBM,''),'N{CTotalPrice}') AS CBM

FROM dbo.EntityContainer ct LEFT JOIN dbo.Shipment sm ON ct.EntityId=sm.Id
LEFT JOIN dbo.MasterData contype ON ct.ContainerTypeId = contype.Id 
LEFT JOIN dbo.MasterData unit ON unit.Id=ct.UnitId 
WHERE ct.EntityId=sm.Id AND sm.Id='{Id}'

SELECT SUM(ct.PKG) AS pkg3, SUM(ct.Weight) AS weight3 , SUM(ct.CBM) AS cbm3

FROM dbo.EntityContainer  ct LEFT JOIN dbo.Shipment shipt ON ct.EntityId=shipt.Id
WHERE shipt.Id='{Id}'

Components.Label: Bill2
Components.Query:
WITH CHARGPM AS 
(SELECT WeightCharge ,
		ValuationCharge,
		Tax,
		TotalDueAgent,
		TotalDueCarrier,
		dbo.ShipmentFreight.Total,
		 PmTypeId ,
		 (case WHEN PmTypeId=1 then (ISNULL(WeightCharge,0)+ISNULL(ValuationCharge,0)+ISNULL(TotalDueCarrier,0)+ISNULL(TotalDueCarrier,0))*(ISNULL(Tax,0)/100) ELSE 0 END ) AS totalcc,
		 (case WHEN PmTypeId=2 then (ISNULL(WeightCharge,0)+ISNULL(ValuationCharge,0)+ISNULL(TotalDueCarrier,0)+ISNULL(TotalDueCarrier,0))*(ISNULL(Tax,0)/100) ELSE 0 END ) AS  totalPP
FROM dbo.ShipmentFreight JOIN dbo.Shipment ON Shipment.Id = ShipmentFreight.ShipmentId 
WHERE Shipment.Id='{Id}'
GROUP BY WeightCharge,PmTypeId,ValuationCharge,Tax,TotalDueAgent,TotalDueCarrier,ShipmentFreight.Total
)
SELECT 
ISNULL(sm.HblNo,'') AS HBLNo,
ISNULL(sm.ShipperDes,'') AS shippertext, 
ISNULL(sm.To1,'') AS t1,
ISNULL(sm.To2,'') AS t2,
ISNULL(sm.to3,'') AS t3,
ISNULL(sm.ByFirstCarrier,'') AS bycarrier,
ISNULL(sm.By1,'') AS b1,
ISNULL(sm.By2,'') AS b2,
ISNULL(sm.Currency,'') AS c1,
ISNULL(sm.CHGSCode,'') AS c2,

CASE WHEN (ISNULL(WT.Name,'')='PPD') THEN 'X' ELSE '' END  AS Wp,
CASE WHEN (ISNULL(WT.Name,'')='COLL') THEN 'X' ELSE '' END  AS Wc,

CASE WHEN (ISNULL(other.Name,'')='COLL') THEN 'X' ELSE '' END  AS OTCCL,
CASE WHEN (ISNULL(other.Name,'')='PPD') THEN 'X' ELSE '' END  AS OTPPD,

ISNULL(sm.DeclaredCarriage,'') AS DVC,
ISNULL(sm.DeclaredCustoms,'') AS DVCs,


ISNULL(sm.CurrencyRatesText,'') AS CurrencyRates ,

ISNULL(sm.ConsigneeDes,'') AS consigneetext, 
ISNULL(sm.NotifyPartyDes,'') AS NotyDes,
(
ISNULL(sm.VesselVoy,'') + ' / ' + isnull(fORMAT(SM.FlightsDate,'dd MMM, yy'),'')
) AS Flight1,
(
ISNULL(sm.CFlights1,'') + ' / ' + ISNULL(FORMAT(sm.CFlights1Date,'dd MMM, yy'),'')
) AS CFlights1,
ISNULL(sm.AmountInsurance,'') AS AmtInsuce,
ISNULL(sm.DetailsGoods,'') AS HandlingInformation,
Format(ISNULL(sm.Quantity,''),'N0') AS Pices,
ISNULL(sm.GW,'') AS GW,
ISNULL(sm.CommodityItemNo,'') As Itno,
ISNULL(sm.KgsLgl,'') AS KGS,
ISNULL(sm.RateClass,'') AS rateclass,
ISNULL(sm.CW,'') AS CW,
CASE WHEN (sm.RateChange IS NULL) THEN 'AS ARRANGED' ELSE CAST(sm.RateChange AS VARCHAR) END AS Rc,
ISNULL(sm.Total,'') AS total,
ISNULL(SM.NatureQuantityGoods,'') AS NatureQuantityGoods ,

CASE WHEN sm.ShippingMark IS NULL OR LEN(sm.ShippingMark)=0 THEN '' ELSE ('SHIPPING MARK:' + CHAR(13) + sm.ShippingMark) end AS SPMK,
ISNULL(sm.OtherCharges,'') AS OtherCharges,


(
CASE WHEN (SELECT  CHARGPM.WeightCharge FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=2 ) = 0 THEN 'AS ARRANGED' 

WHEN (SELECT  CHARGPM.WeightCharge FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=2 ) IS NULL THEN '' 
ELSE
 CAST((SELECT  CHARGPM.WeightCharge FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=2 )AS VARCHAR) END 
 ) AS WChargePP,

(
CASE WHEN (SELECT  CHARGPM.WeightCharge FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=1 ) = 0 THEN 'AS ARRANGED' 
WHEN (SELECT  CHARGPM.WeightCharge FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=1 ) IS NULL THEN '' 
ELSE
 CAST((SELECT  CHARGPM.WeightCharge FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=1 )AS VARCHAR) END 
) AS WChargeCC ,
(
CASE WHEN (SELECT ValuationCharge  FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=1 ) = 0 THEN 'AS ARRANGED' 
WHEN (SELECT  CHARGPM.ValuationCharge FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=1 ) IS NULL THEN '' 
ELSE
 CAST((SELECT  CHARGPM.ValuationCharge FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=1 )AS VARCHAR) END 
) AS VChargeCC ,
(
CASE WHEN (SELECT ValuationCharge  FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=2 ) = 0 THEN 'AS ARRANGED' 
WHEN (SELECT  CHARGPM.ValuationCharge FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=2 ) IS NULL THEN '' 
ELSE
 CAST((SELECT  CHARGPM.ValuationCharge FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=2 )AS VARCHAR) END 
) AS VChargePP ,
(
CASE WHEN (SELECT CHARGPM.Tax  FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=2 ) = 0 THEN '0' 
WHEN (SELECT  CHARGPM.Tax FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=2 ) IS NULL THEN '' 
ELSE
 CAST((SELECT  CHARGPM.Tax FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=2 )AS VARCHAR) END 
) AS TAXPP ,
(
CASE WHEN (SELECT CHARGPM.Tax  FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=1 ) = 0 THEN '0' 
WHEN (SELECT  CHARGPM.Tax FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=1 ) IS NULL THEN '' 
ELSE
 CAST((SELECT  CHARGPM.Tax FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=1 )AS VARCHAR) END 
) AS TAXCC ,
(
CASE WHEN (SELECT CHARGPM.TotalDueAgent  FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=1 ) = 0 THEN '0' 
WHEN (SELECT  CHARGPM.TotalDueAgent FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=1 ) IS NULL THEN '' 
ELSE
 CAST((SELECT  CHARGPM.TotalDueAgent FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=1 )AS VARCHAR) END 
) AS TtDueAgCC ,
(
CASE WHEN (SELECT CHARGPM.TotalDueAgent  FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=2 ) = 0 THEN 'AS ARRANGED' 
WHEN (SELECT  CHARGPM.TotalDueAgent FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=2 ) IS NULL THEN '' 
ELSE
 CAST((SELECT  CHARGPM.TotalDueAgent FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=2 )AS VARCHAR) END 
) AS TDueAgPP ,
(
CASE WHEN (SELECT CHARGPM.TotalDueAgent  FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=1 ) = 0 THEN 'AS ARRANGED' 
WHEN (SELECT  CHARGPM.TotalDueAgent FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=1 ) IS NULL THEN '' 
ELSE
 CAST((SELECT  CHARGPM.TotalDueAgent FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=1 )AS VARCHAR) END 
) AS TotalDueAgentCC ,
(
CASE WHEN (SELECT CHARGPM.TotalDueCarrier  FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=1 ) = 0 THEN 'AS ARRANGED' 
WHEN (SELECT  CHARGPM.TotalDueCarrier FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=1 ) IS NULL THEN '' 
ELSE
 CAST((SELECT  CHARGPM.TotalDueCarrier FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=1 )AS VARCHAR) END 
) AS TDueCarCC,
(
CASE WHEN (SELECT CHARGPM.TotalDueCarrier  FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=2 ) = 0 THEN 'AS ARRANGED' 
WHEN (SELECT  CHARGPM.TotalDueCarrier FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=2 ) IS NULL THEN '' 
ELSE
 CAST((SELECT  CHARGPM.TotalDueCarrier FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=2 )AS VARCHAR) END 
) AS TotalDueCarrierPP,
(
CASE WHEN (SELECT CHARGPM.Total  FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=2 ) = 0 THEN '0' 
WHEN (SELECT  CHARGPM.Total FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=2 ) IS NULL THEN 'As ARRANGED' 
ELSE
 CAST((SELECT  CHARGPM.Total FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=2 )AS VARCHAR) END 
) AS TotalPP,
(
CASE WHEN (SELECT CHARGPM.Total  FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=1 ) = 0 THEN '0' 
WHEN (SELECT  CHARGPM.Total FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=1 ) IS NULL THEN 'As ARRANGED' 
ELSE
 CAST((SELECT  CHARGPM.Total FROM CHARGPM WHERE CHARGPM.PmTypeId=1 )AS VARCHAR) END 
) AS TotalCC,
ISNULL(sm.CurrencyRatesText,'') AS CurrRates,
ISNULL(sm.CCCharges,'') AS Chargeindes,
ISNULL(place.Name,'') AS placeissue,

FORMAT(ISNULL(sm.IssueDate,''),'dd MMM, yy') AS dateissue,

ISNULL(POl.Name,'') AS AOD,
ISNULL(POD.Name,'') AS PODName,
ISNULL(destination.Name,'') AS Destination,
isnull(payableat.Name,'') as Payable,
isnull(sm.NumberOriginalIdText,'') AS numberbill,


ISNULL( sm.ForDeliveryGoodsDes,'') AS Deliverygoods,
ISNULL(charge.Name,'') AS Chageterm,

ISNULL(receipt.Name,'') AS placereceipt,
ISNULL(deliveryplace.Name,'') AS deliveryplace ,
ISNULL(typemove.Name,'') AS Typeofmove,
ISNULL(caluse.Name,'') AS clause,
FORMAT(ISNULL(sm.SaillingDate,''),'dd MMM, yyyy') AS saillingdate,
ISNULL(sm.ContainerText,'') AS quantityofcontainer,
ISNULL(unit.Name,'') AS Unitpkg



FROM dbo.Shipment sm LEFT JOIN dbo.Terminal POL ON POL.Id = sm.PolId
LEFT JOIN dbo.Terminal POD ON POD.Id = sm.PodId
LEFT JOIN dbo.MasterData WT ON WT.Id = sm.WTVALId
LEFT JOIN dbo.MasterData other ON other.Id = sm.OtherId
LEFT JOIN dbo.Terminal destination ON destination.Id = sm.FinalDestinationId
LEFT JOIN dbo.MasterData payableat ON payableat.Id = sm.FreightPayableId
LEFT JOIN dbo.MasterData charge ON charge.Id = sm.FreightChargeId
LEFT JOIN dbo.MasterData place ON place.Id = sm.PlaceIssueId 
LEFT JOIN dbo.Terminal receipt ON receipt.Id = sm.PlaceReceiptId
LEFT JOIN dbo.Terminal deliveryplace ON deliveryplace.Id = sm.PlaceDeliveryId
LEFT JOIN dbo.MasterData typemove ON typemove.Id = sm.TypeMoveId
LEFT JOIN dbo.MasterData caluse ON caluse.Id = sm.ClauseId
LEFT JOIN dbo.MasterData unit ON unit.Id=sm.UnitId
WHERE   sm.Id='{Id}'

Components.Label: Air Cargo Manifest
Components.Query:
SELECT 
sm.Code AS code,
FORMAT(sm.EtdDate,'MMM dd, yyy') AS etd, 
FORMAT(sm.EtaDate,'MMM dd, yyy') AS eta,
pol.Name AS POLName,sm.VesselVoy AS Fligt,
pod.Name AS PODName

FROM dbo.Shipment sm LEFT JOIN dbo.Terminal pol ON sm.PolId=pol.Id 
LEFT JOIN dbo.Terminal pod ON sm.PodId=pod.Id

WHERE  sm.Id='{Id}'



SELECT sm.Code AS Fileno, 
FORMAT(sm.EtdDate,'dd MMM, yy') AS ETD,
sm.VesselVoy AS FilghtNo,
POL.Name AS POL,
POD.Name AS POD,
(CASE WHEN sm.ParentId IS NULL THEN 'M' ELSE 'H' END) AS AW,
CASE WHEN sm.StatusId=1 THEN sm.MblNo ELSE sm.HblNo END AS AWbNO,
CASE WHEN sm.StatusId=1 THEN 
CASE WHEN sm.FreightId IS NOT NULL THEN 'FREIGHT ' + freight.Name ELSE '' END
ELSE 	CASE WHEN sm.WTVALId IS NOT NULL THEN 'FREIGHT ' + freighthbl.Description ELSE '' END					
END  AS FREIGHTTYPE ,
ISNULL(SM.Quantity,'') AS Qty,
ISNULL(unit.Name,'') AS Unit,
ISNULL(sm.GW,'') AS GW,
CASE WHEN sm.StatusId=1 THEN 
(SELECT COUNT(*) AS Quantybill FROM dbo.Shipment WHERE dbo.Shipment.Code=sm.Code AND dbo.Shipment.ParentId IS NOT NULL)
 ELSE 1 END AS Qbill, 
 sm.CW AS CW,
 CASE WHEN ISNULL(sm.ShipperDes,'')='' THEN (pn.CompanyName + CHAR(10) + pn.AddressInv)
 ELSE  sm.ShipperDes  END  AS Shipper,

 CASE WHEN ISNULL(sm.ConsigneeDes,'')= NULL THEN agent.Name + CHAR(13) + agent.Address ELSE sm.ConsigneeDes END  AS consignee,

 CASE WHEN sm.StatusId=1 THEN (agent.CompanyName + CHAR(10) + agent.Address ) ELSE
 ISNULL(sm.ConsigneeDes,'') END AS Consignee,
 ISNULL(sm.NotifyPartyDes,'') AS Notify,
 CASE WHEN sm.StatusId=1 THEN 'CONSOL CARGO AND DOCUMENTS ATTACHED' ELSE ISNULL(sm.NatureQuantityGoods,'') END AS Descripton
 FROM dbo.Shipment sm LEFT JOIN dbo.MasterData POL ON POL.Id = sm.PolId 
LEFT JOIN dbo.MasterData POD ON POD.Id = sm.PodId 
LEFT JOIN dbo.MasterData freight ON freight.Id = sm.FreightId
LEFT JOIN dbo.MasterData freighthbl ON freighthbl.Id = sm.WTVALId
LEFT JOIN dbo.MasterData unit ON unit.Id=sm.UnitId
LEFT JOIN dbo.Partner agent ON agent.Id = sm.AgentId
LEFT JOIN dbo.[User] us ON us.Id = sm.InsertedBy
LEFT JOIN dbo.Partner pn ON pn.Id = us.CompanyId

WHERE 
sm.ParentId='{Id}' OR sm.Id='{Id}'
